    {
      "instruction": "<p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p>",
      "order": 2,
