            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>white</strong> <strong>long grain rice</strong> to a pot with a lid with 225ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml] </span>[450ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and the<strong> outer lemongrass</strong> <strong>layers </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once done, remove from the heat and set aside (lid on) to steam until serving – this is your <strong>lemongrass rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1632300795931-x200.jpg",
